survey_response.review_text: I had high fever and was extremely anxious due to my exams. I went to Dr. Dhuri. As soon as I walked in he greeted me and made me feel comfortable. Then he asked me a bit about my self to calm me down and then took my temperature. While measuring he told me that I'm fine its just the anxiety that was freaking my out. This gave me a moral boost and I felt courageous. He then prescribed me the medicines and was courteous enough to walk me out of the clinic. He is a not just GREAT DOCTOR but also a GENTLEMAN.
Very friendly doctor with accurate treatment and diagnosis. Recommended for everyone to visit . Very caring with good nature and provides the best cure.
